{"actor":"lennartbinkowski","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T15:16:34Z","event_type":"claimed","id":17,"issue_id":"AdiabaticGrover-1ba","new_value":"{\"assignee\":\"lennartbinkowski\",\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"AdiabaticGrover-1ba\",\"title\":\"Define IsStoquastic: WHT of b is non-positive off the DC component\",\"description\":\"IsStoquastic n b := ∀ k : BoolVec n, k ≠ 0 → (∑_z b z * (-1)^bitDot k z) ≤ 0. This is the condition B̂(k) ≤ 0 for k ≠ 0.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lennart.binkowski@itp.uni-hannover.de\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-05T13:51:10Z\",\"created_by\":\"lennartbinkowski\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T13:51:10Z\"}"}
