{"actor":"lennartbinkowski","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T15:16:36Z","event_type":"claimed","id":21,"issue_id":"AdiabaticGrover-9j4","new_value":"{\"assignee\":\"lennartbinkowski\",\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"AdiabaticGrover-9j4\",\"title\":\"Axiomatize Perron-Frobenius for irreducible non-positive off-diagonal matrices\",\"description\":\"axiom perron_frobenius: real symmetric matrix with strictly negative off-diagonal entries has a simple minimum eigenvalue with a strictly positive eigenvector. Check Mathlib first (search for PerronFrobenius, Irreducible, Matrix.pos_eigenvalue); axiomatize if absent.\",\"status\":\"closed\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"lennart.binkowski@itp.uni-hannover.de\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-05T13:51:23Z\",\"created_by\":\"lennartbinkowski\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T14:02:51Z\",\"closed_at\":\"2026-03-05T14:02:51Z\",\"close_reason\":\"Axiomatized Perron-Frobenius in PerronFrobenius.lean\"}"}
